html:
Catching last rays of sun
Like birds on a branch
Lacking papers
To prove to the blind and deaf
Inspected by bees
Carying keys on the neck
Smoking tobacco
In a park nearby
Papers or death!
Yells the history
The history
That is dead without them
And leafs keep on falling
On the ground
The ground that prepares
For upcoming winter
title: Price of anarchism
